          </section>
        </section>

        <section><title>spin button (ROLE_SPIN_BUTTON)</title>
          <para>A spin button is a single line item that contains a list of
            choices the user can select from.</para>
          <section><title>Braille</title>
            <para>The verbose and brief modes will show the label followed
              by the item followed by the word "spin."</para>
            <itemizedlist>
              <listitem>
                <para>Verbose Example: Red: 57 spin</para>
              </listitem>
              <listitem>
                <para>Brief Example: Red: 57 spin</para>
              </listitem>
            </itemizedlist>
          </section>

