        <section><title>tear off menu item (ROLE_TEAR_OFF_MENU_ITEM)</title>
          <para>A tear off menu item allows a menu to be removed from a menu
            bar and shown in its own window.</para>

          <section><title>Braille</title>    

            <para>All menus items from a single menu will be shown at
              the same time (see ROLE_MENU).  The menu item with focus
              (if there is one) will be the most meaningful object and
              it will also have the braille cursor.  The touch cursors
              will activate the associated item.  Tear off menu items
              will be shown with "---" as their label.</para>
     
            <itemizedlist>
              <listitem>
                <para>Verbose Example: file menu --- _ new _ save _ quit _ ...</para>
              </listitem>
              <listitem>
                <para>Brief Example: file menu --- _ new _ save _ quit _ ...</para>
              </listitem>
            </itemizedlist>
          </section>

